{"tid":1459520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警黑勾結 將軍澳常德三不管 罷食","createTime":"2019-08-12T17:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T09:12:37.000Z","uid":214761,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1304614d1d2cef3dfae342a99f053c6ee7beaf77","tid":1459520,"uid":214761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"近排個個話警黑勾結 點解仲會有將軍澳人走去食尚德<br />\n明明冇耐前先係咁報尚德有黑社會喺後面操縱 仲有咁多人去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收得貴衛生環境又差 又唔係特別好食 仲要冇小販牌<br />\n明明阻曬街但又冇警察做野 擺明係克警同黑社會傾曬數<br />\n所以希望將軍澳罷食尚德<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"2bbd1d924bef501e22ebbb527c98ef7482abc856","tid":1459520,"uid":206120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"啲人成日食完煙又直接煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf6dab5dbaa274203cc2041292066f5452683d0","tid":1459520,"uid":214761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:57:13.000Z","msg":"推到有人罷食唯止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78a7bd53ca0ca626567af2229d97c2a634b55c7","tid":1459520,"uid":205055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"個日係尚德食完飯肚痛<br />\n都唔知係唔係用大陸個d黑心肉<br />\n尚德宵夜不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持罷食罷到佢地同黑社會收皮<br />\n斷佢地財路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5578483c23b54d6ecb5ec356b7e3a8e8b61f8de7","tid":1459520,"uid":81722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"支持樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc67aa4ecd4c1a01aec8adcc57a10453db332f4","tid":1459520,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"推返上黎先。其實本身我都非常鍾意食街邊檔, 但尚德果啲真係完全幫襯唔落。講背景, 呢啲檔同黑幫冇關係我就唔信。講衛生, 我明白街邊車仔檔講衛生係冇可能, 但尚德果啲車仔檔既衛生唔係一般的差, 係好撚柒污糟果隻。講價錢, 我只係幫襯過一檔熟食, 超貴, 同店舖價錢相差唔遠, 記憶中大約只比茶記餐廳平4%左右重要係冇野飲（ 飲品只係用黎做價錢比較 ）唔洗俾舖租都要收咁貴, 唔係要俾陀地就即係食水深, 所以其他檔相信都唔會平。從前年幫襯過至今我都冇再幫襯過, 以後都唔會再幫襯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35c501bab41631c3c952cf4dc80bd9a4c2c2a0e","tid":1459520,"uid":214761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人有留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}